import React from "react"; import { Container, Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap"; import { contactConfig } from "../content_option"; export default function ContactUs() { return ( < Container className = "Cont" > < Row className = "sec_sp" > < Col lg = "5" className = "mb-5" > < h3 className = "color_sec py-4 px-4" > Contact Us < /h3> < address > < strong > Inspections < /strong>{" "} 

        <
        a href = { `mailto:${ contactConfig.User_Email }` } >  {contactConfig.YOUR_FONE} <
        /a> | { contactConfig.User_Email }<
        br / >
        <
        br / >
        <
        strong > Franchising < /strong>{" "}

        br / >
        <
        br / >
        <

        a href = { `mailto:${contactConfig.User_Email}` } > { contactConfig.Your_Phone}  <

        /address>
     
        <
        /Col>

        input className = "form-control"

        placeholder = "(123)456-789"

        /Col> <

        /Col> <
        /Row> <
        div className = "mb-4" >

        placeholder = "Please type it in here..."
        rows = "5"
        required >
        < /textarea> <
        /div>

        <
        br / >
        <
        Row className = "mb-4" >
        <
        Col lg = "12"

        button className = "btn "

        Submit <
        /button> <
        /Col> <
        /Row> <
        /form> <
        /Col> <
        /Row> <
        br / >
        <
        br / >
        <
        Row >
        <
        footer >

        h4 > Subscribe to our User_Emails < /h4> <
        p > Enter your User_Email address to recieve the latest notifictions, newsleers and updates from WIN! < /p> <
        Row className = "Foot" >

        input className = "form-control rounded"

        required


        /

        /Col> <

        <
        button className = "btn ac_btn"

        /Row> 

        <
        /footer> <
        /Row> <
        /Container>
    );
